{
  "page": "Yellow emperors",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>yellow emperors</b> are an ancient ruling dynasty of the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Empire_of_Yi_Ti\" title=\"Golden Empire of Yi Ti\">Golden Empire of Yi Ti</a>. The dynasty fell a thousand years ago. However, the <a href=\"/index.php/Sorcerer_lord\" title=\"Sorcerer lord\">sorcerer lord</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Carcosa\" title=\"Carcosa\">Carcosa</a> claims to be the sixty-ninth yellow emperor. The family name of the yellow emperors is <b>Chai</b>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafyi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafyi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_yellow_emperors\">Known yellow emperors</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Yellow_emperors&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known yellow emperors\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/God-Emperor\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"God-Emperor\">Emperor</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Chai_Duq\" title=\"Chai Duq\">Chai Duq</a>, fourth yellow emperor</li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Sorcerer_lord\" title=\"Sorcerer lord\">sorcerer lord</a> of Carcosa, claiming to be the sixty-ninth yellow emperor</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_notes\">References and notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Yellow_emperors&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafyi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafyi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Yi Ti.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403164721\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.008 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.009 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 100/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8538/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 297/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 43/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 522/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    5.441      1 -total\n 73.74%    4.012      1 Template:Ref\n 46.48%    2.529      1 Template:Ref/core\n 24.13%    1.313      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:19674-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403164721 and revision id 297570\n -->\n",
